					                <li class="p_relative d_block fs_16 lh_22 fw_normal pl_20 mb_10"><b>Legitimate interest:</b> the interest of our business in conducting and managing our business to enable us to give you the best service/product and the best and most secure experience</li>
					                <li class="p_relative d_block fs_16 lh_22 fw_normal pl_20 mb_10"><b>Performance of contract:</b> the processing your data where it is necessary to be able to fulfill a contract to which you are a party or to take steps at your request before entering into such a contract</li>
					                <li class="p_relative d_block fs_16 lh_22 fw_normal pl_20 mb_10"><b>Comply with a legal obligation:</b> if required, we will process your personal data in a way that is compliant with and adheres to the relevant law(s)</li>
